@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>


<p>
    This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and disclose your personal information when you use our room rental platform. By using our platform, you consent to the collection, use, and disclosure of your personal information as described in this Privacy Policy.
</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>

<p>
    We collect personal information that you provide to us when you create an account, list a room, make a booking, or communicate with other users. This may include your name, email address, phone number, and payment information.
</p>

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>

<p>
    We use your personal information to facilitate room bookings, communicate with you, improve our platform, and comply with legal obligations. We may also use your information for marketing purposes, but you can opt out of receiving marketing communications at any time.
</p>

<h2>Information Sharing and Disclosure</h2>

<p>
    We may share your personal information with other users for the purpose of facilitating room bookings. We may also share your information with service providers who assist us in operating our platform. We do not sell your personal information to third parties.
</p>

<h2>Security</h2>

<p>
    We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or alteration. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, so we cannot guarantee absolute security.
</p>

<h2>Changes to this Privacy Policy</h2>

<p>
    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the updated Privacy Policy on our platform. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.
</p>

<h2>Contact Us</h2>

<p>
    If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at privacy@roomrentalplatform.com.
</p>

